trans-unit.source: Defines identifiers for the standard set of commands that are available to most applications.
trans-unit.target: Definerer identifikatorer for settet med kommandoer som er tilgjengelige for de fleste programmer.

trans-unit.source: This class defines <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.CommandID> identifiers for standard commands that are available to designers.
trans-unit.target: Denne klassen definerer <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.CommandID>identifikatorer for standard kommandoer som er tilgjengelige for utviklere.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.CommandID>

trans-unit.source: To add a command from the StandardCommands class to a designer menu, you must call the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IMenuCommandService.AddCommand%2A> method of an <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IMenuCommandService> and add a <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.MenuCommand> that contains a <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.CommandID> from StandardCommands.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil legge til en kommando fra klassen StandardCommands designer-menyen, må du kalle den <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IMenuCommandService.AddCommand%2A>-metoden til et <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IMenuCommandService>og legge til en <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.MenuCommand>som inneholder en <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.CommandID>fra StandardCommands.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.CommandID> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.MenuCommand> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IMenuCommandService> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IMenuCommandService.AddCommand%2A>

trans-unit.source: Gets the first of a set of verbs.
trans-unit.target: Henter først av et sett med verb.

trans-unit.source: This is a special <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.CommandID> that identifies the first of a set of designer verbs.
trans-unit.target: Dette er en spesiell <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.CommandID>som identifiserer først av et sett med designer verb.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.CommandID>

trans-unit.source: The Visual Studio Windows Forms Designer automatically maps designer verbs to the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IDesigner.Verbs%2A> property on <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IDesigner>, so generally you do not need to access this command.
trans-unit.target: Visual Studio Windows Forms Designer automatisk tilordner designer verbene som den <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IDesigner.Verbs%2A>egenskapen for <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IDesigner>, så vanligvis du ikke trenger å få tilgang til denne kommandoen.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IDesigner> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IDesigner.Verbs%2A>

trans-unit.source: All designer verbs for an object become commands with a <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.CommandID> within a sequential range of IDs that begins with VerbFirst and ends with <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.StandardCommands.VerbLast>.
trans-unit.target: Alle designer verb for et objekt, blir kommandoer med en <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.CommandID>i en sekvensiell serie IDer som begynner med VerbFirst og slutter på <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.StandardCommands.VerbLast>.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.StandardCommands.VerbLast> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.CommandID>

trans-unit.source: Gets the last of a set of verbs.
trans-unit.target: Henter sist av et sett med verb.

trans-unit.source: This is a special <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.CommandID> that identifies the last of a set of designer verbs.
trans-unit.target: Dette er en spesiell <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.CommandID>som identifiserer sist av et sett med designer verb.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.CommandID>

trans-unit.source: The Visual Studio Windows Forms Designer automatically maps designer verbs to the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IDesigner.Verbs%2A> property on <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IDesigner>, so generally you do not need to access this command.
trans-unit.target: Visual Studio Windows Forms Designer automatisk tilordner designer verbene som den <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IDesigner.Verbs%2A>egenskapen for <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IDesigner>, så vanligvis du ikke trenger å få tilgang til denne kommandoen.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IDesigner> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IDesigner.Verbs%2A>

trans-unit.source: All designer verbs for an object become commands with a <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.CommandID> within a sequential range of IDs that begins with <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.StandardCommands.VerbFirst> and ends with VerbLast.
trans-unit.target: Alle designer verb for et objekt, blir kommandoer med en <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.CommandID>i en sekvensiell serie IDer som begynner med <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.StandardCommands.VerbFirst>og slutter på VerbLast.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.StandardCommands.VerbFirst> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.CommandID>
